description: Add a special touch to your grazing platter with a homemade roasted beetroot dip. This vibrant dip is easy to make and perfect with fresh veggie sticks.
name: Easy Beetroot Hummus Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g Woolworths cooked & peeled fresh beetroot

recipeInstructions.text: Spoon mixture into a medium bowl. Scatter with sesame seeds and drizzle with extra oil. Serve with cucumber, capsicum, radish, snow peas and carrots.
